OL,3,CNI's top judge: Domestic abusers
OL,4,Caren't being let off lightly
OL,6,FWe discovered in the most recent
OL,7,Ffigures in 2023 there were a total of
OL,8,F1970 convictions for domestic abuse.
OL,10,FOf those, two thirds received a non-
OL,11,Fcustodial sentence and only a third of
OL,12,Fthose found guilty spent any time
OL,13,Fbehind bars.
OL,15,FOf those who did serve time, only a
OL,16,Fminority (99), got more than 12 months.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/17
