OL,3,CNI's top judge: Domestic abusers
OL,4,Caren't being let off lightly
OL,6,FDame Keegan, however, told UTV she
OL,7,Fsupported changes to sentencing
OL,8,Fpractice.
OL,10,F"The first is to increase the
OL,11,Fjurisdiction of the Magistrates Court,
OL,12,Fand that's something that's on the
OL,13,Fagenda at the Criminal Justice Board
OL,14,Fto give Magistrates greater sentencing
OL,15,Fpowers.
OL,26,@rD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/17
