OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F449A1743013875
OL,3,CNI's top judge: Domestic abusers
OL,4,Caren't being let off lightly
OL,6,F"Society has clearly spoken in
OL,7,Frelation to the fact that this
OL,8,Fbehavior isn't normal, isn't
OL,9,Ftolerated, and sentences should be
OL,10,Fhigher. And I've said that myself in a
OL,11,Frecent case, but it has to get to the
OL,12,Fhigher court for that," she added.
OL,14,F"The third element, I think that will
OL,15,Faffect the statistics you've mentioned
OL,16,Fis when some of these new offences are
OL,17,Fprosecuted and are coming through the
OL,18,Fsystem, I think you will see a change.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@WO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/17
