OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F449A1743013875
OL,3,CNI's top judge: Domestic abusers
OL,4,Caren't being let off lightly
OL,6,F"I think it's really good that this is
OL,7,Fon the agenda and has been spoken
OL,8,Fabout in the community by the media,
OL,9,Fby commentators. We do have a system
OL,10,Fnow that has reacted to the problem.
OL,11,FThe new legislation that we have:
OL,12,Fcoercive control is now recognized as
OL,13,Fan aspect of violence against women,
OL,14,Fwhich is positive,"she said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/17
