OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F449A1743013875
OL,3,CNI's top judge: Domestic abusers
OL,4,Caren't being let off lightly
OL,6,F"Non-Fatal strangulation as a criminal
OL,7,Foffence, domestic abuse as a criminal
OL,8,Foffence. So we have found the courts
OL,9,Fare gradually having to look at these
OL,10,Fcases. I'm not sure they have filtered
OL,11,Fthrough as yet to completion, but
OL,12,Fthey're in the system.
OL,14,F"So law has reacted by legislation and
OL,15,Fwe also have an understanding that
OL,16,Fthis remains a problem in our society."
OL,18,FBut the Chief Justice insisted it was
OL,19,Fnot just a problem for the courts.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUxD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/17
