OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F449A1743013875
OL,3,CNI's top judge: Domestic abusers
OL,4,Caren't being let off lightly
OL,6,F"It goes right back to schools in
OL,7,Frelation to healthy relationships.
OL,8,FWhat's normal, what's not normal,
OL,9,Fwhich means that as a society we have
OL,10,Fgot to pick this up. I think I would
OL,11,Falso say that this is very much part
OL,12,Fof a conversation that all the
OL,13,Fcriminal justice partners are having,"
OL,14,Fshe said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/17
