OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F449A1743013875
OL,3,CNI's top judge: Domestic abusers
OL,4,Caren't being let off lightly
OL,6,F"So I sit on the criminal justice
OL,7,Fboard with the Justice Minister, with
OL,8,Fthe Chief Constable, with the police,
OL,9,Fwith lawyers And collectively, we are
OL,10,Flooking at better ways to deal with
OL,11,Fthis issue. And our message is really
OL,12,Frobust that there is a zero tolerance
OL,13,Ffor this type of behavior. It's not
OL,14,Fnormal. It will be prosecuted. I think
OL,15,Fthat shows by virtue of the fact that
OL,16,Fthere have been more complaints and
OL,17,Fmore convictions.
OL,19,F"So the message is getting out there.
OL,20,FIt's not something we should sit on
OL,21,Four laurels about.
OL,26,@nD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/17
