OL,3,CNI's top judge: Domestic abusers
OL,4,Caren't being let off lightly
OL,6,F"But for me, it's positive that we're
OL,7,Fspeaking about it. It remains on the
OL,8,Fagenda. The courts will react to it,"
OL,9,Fshe added.
OL,11,FNorthern Ireland's top judge rejected
OL,12,Fclaims that perpetrators are being let
OL,13,Foff the hook in light of our freedom
OL,14,Fof information request to the
OL,15,FDepartment of Justice which showed low
OL,16,Flevels of custodial sentences for
OL,17,Fdomestic abuse crimes.
OL,26,@pD@eO]
