PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F449A1743013875
OL,3,CNI's top judge: Domestic abusers
OL,4,Caren't being let off lightly
OL,6,F"I think it's something whereby both
OL,7,Fgenders as judges need education on
OL,8,Fwhat's the right language to use? How
OL,9,Fdo you avoid retraumatising victims in
OL,10,Fthe process? So training's been good
OL,11,Fon that, and it's something I'm
OL,12,Fcommitted to on an ongoing basis," she
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,FWhen asked about the issue of legacy
OL,16,FDame Keegan said she remained of the
OL,17,Fview that it was a societal problem.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G15/17
