OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F449A1743013875
OL,3,CNI's top judge: Domestic abusers
OL,4,Caren't being let off lightly
OL,6,F"I think there's a piece about
OL,7,Freconciliation in our society. While
OL,8,Fthe legal side of things is ongoing I
OL,9,Fthink it would be wrong for me to give
OL,10,Fany firm opinion on that, safe to say
OL,11,Fwe're still dealing with it.
OL,13,F"But there's a collective
OL,14,Fresponsibility beyond the courts and
OL,15,Fthe lawyers to try and deal with
OL,16,Fissues that are there for people and
OL,17,Ffamilies over many decades and people
OL,18,Fneed answers to the questions that
OL,19,Fthey have," she said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU{D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G16/17
