OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F449A1743013875
OL,3,CNI's top judge: Domestic abusers
OL,4,Caren't being let off lightly
OL,6,F"I think we have to come up with a way
OL,7,Fof trying to deal with people's cases
OL,8,Fand issues. And I think, as I've said
OL,9,Fbefore, only a fraction of the victims
OL,10,Fof the troubles issues are before the
OL,11,Fcourt, either by the small cohort of
OL,12,Finquests that were directed under the
OL,13,Ffive year plan or in civil cases.
OL,15,F"There are many more people out there
OL,16,Fwho have also suffered, and that's why
OL,17,Fit's a societal issue. And that's why
OL,18,Fit's broader than the courts."
